.DT
add_player_title
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_player_title

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_player_title -  This method adds the players title into the list of allowed titles.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_player_title(string title)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^title%^RESET%^ - the title to add into the list
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the title was added successfuly, 0 if it exists
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/family.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds the players title into the list of allowed titles.
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
player->add_player_title("lord");

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_player_title(), remove_player_title()
.EP

